ABOUT MAYBE STAYING.

90
00:03:32,413 --> 00:03:35,449
- THAT'S ALL I HAVE TO HEAR.

91
00:03:35,483 --> 00:03:38,686
YOU WON'T LIVE
TO REGRET THIS.

92
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:41,289
- UNLESS ANDY CAN UN-KISS ANN,

93
