THEN I'M NOT GONNA CHANGE
MY MIND.

94
00:03:44,024 --> 00:03:45,759
BUT IF HE WANTS TO TAKE
MY DUMB SISTER

95
00:03:45,793 --> 00:03:47,295
TO HER DUMB DANCE CLASS,

96
00:03:47,328 --> 00:03:51,299
THEN I'M NOT GONNA
DUMB STOP HIM.

97
00:03:51,332 --> 00:03:54,268
- CRAZY IRA AND THE DOUCHE--
93.7.

98
00:03:54,302 --> 00:03:56,704
- YOU KNOW WHY
I'D NEVER BE AN ASTRONAUT?

99
00:03:56,737 --> 00:03:59,707
TWO WORDS--SPACE FARTS.

100
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:02,543
YOU CAN'T ROLL DOWN
THE WINDOW OF THE SHUTTLE.

101
00:04:02,576 --> 00:04:03,577
AM I RIGHT, FOLKS?

102
00:04:03,611 --> 00:04:05,313
- HOUSTON, WE HAVE A...
[farting]

103
00:04:05,346 --> 00:04:07,548
NOW, WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT THAT, NEIL ARMSTRONG?

104
00:04:07,581 --> 00:04:10,718
THAT'S ONE SMALL...
[farting] FOR MAN.

105
00:04:10,751 --> 00:04:13,921
ONE GIANT...
[farting] FOR MANKIND.

106
00:04:13,954 --> 00:04:15,889
ALL RIGHT, SWITCHING GEARS
HERE NOW.

107
00:04:15,923 --> 00:04:18,759
WE GOT LESLIE KNOPE
AND TOM HAVERFART...

108
00:04:18,792 --> 00:04:21,429
[farting] AND, UH, BEN WYATT,
AND THEY'RE IN THE HIZZY

109
00:04:21,462 --> 00:04:25,566
TO TALK ABOUT AN UPCOMING EVENT
