AND SPOILER ALERT--

115
00:04:36,810 --> 00:04:38,912
IT'S GONNA HAVE
THE BEST CORN MAZE EVER.

116
00:04:38,946 --> 00:04:41,549
- YOU LOST YOUR VIRGINITY IN
A CORN MAZE, DIDN'T YOU, DOUCHE?

117
00:04:41,582 --> 00:04:42,783
- OH, THAT'S RIGHT,
TO YOUR MOM.

118
00:04:42,816 --> 00:04:44,618
[woman moaning]

119
00:04:44,652 --> 00:04:47,421
- CRAZY IRA,
CLEAN YOUR ROOM!

120
00:04:47,455 --> 00:04:49,790
- THERE'S ALSO
GONNA BE HAYRIDES.

121
00:04:49,823 --> 00:04:52,059
- "HEY, RIDE ME"...IS WHAT
CRAZY IRA'S MOM SAID.

122
00:04:52,092 --> 00:04:53,727
- STOP IT!

123
00:04:53,761 --> 00:04:55,095
[woman moaning]

124
00:04:55,128 --> 00:04:57,798
- CHINA JOE, YOU ARE A POET.

125
00:04:57,831 --> 00:04:59,467
[laughing]

126
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,834
- MY BIRD IS MISSING.

127
00:05:00,868 --> 00:05:02,703
I NEED A PERMIT
TO POST SIGNS.

128
00:05:02,736 --> 00:05:05,406
- OH, LET ME JUST LOOK
FOR THAT FORM.

129
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:07,808
- THERE'S NO TIME!
HE CAN FLY!

130
00:05:07,841 --> 00:05:09,877
- NINE THINGS
APRIL HATES TO DO.

131
00:05:09,910 --> 00:05:12,413
"NUMBER ONE, RUN
THE PERMITS DESK FOR AN HOUR."

132
00:05:12,446 --> 00:05:13,614
THAT'S NO PROBLEM.

133
00:05:13,647 --> 00:05:16,450
