138
00:05:25,893 --> 00:05:28,829
- YEAH.
- HENRY.

139
00:05:28,862 --> 00:05:30,764
- WHY ARE YOU WORKING
THE PERMITS DESK?

140
00:05:30,798 --> 00:05:34,868
AND WHY WAS THAT CHILD
CLUBBING YOUR NUGGETS?

141
00:05:34,902 --> 00:05:37,838
- I'M TRYING TO STOP APRIL
FROM TAKING A JOB WITH CHRIS,

142
00:05:37,871 --> 00:05:41,475
