- SHE SAID IT MIGHT.

144
00:05:44,077 --> 00:05:46,614
BUT IT'S ALL I GOT, MAN.

145
00:05:47,815 --> 00:05:49,883
- GIVE ME THE LIST.

146
00:05:49,917 --> 00:05:51,118
I'LL HELP YOU.

147
00:05:51,151 --> 00:05:54,388
- OH, MY GOD.
THANK YOU.

148
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:58,158
- YOU GOT IT.

149
00:05:58,191 --> 00:05:59,960
NO, I DON'T CARE
ABOUT THEIR RELATIONSHIP.

150
00:05:59,993 --> 00:06:02,796
I JUST DON'T WANT
TO LOSE APRIL.

151
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:06,800
I WOULD NEVER BE ABLE TO FIND
A WORSE ASSISTANT.

152
00:06:06,834 --> 00:06:08,502
- OKAY, THANKS, LESLIE.

153
00:06:08,536 --> 00:06:10,938
