THE SCENES KIND OF GUY.

157
00:06:17,811 --> 00:06:20,948
- WELL, IT'S EITHER COME WITH US
OR GET IN THE SPANK CHAIR.

158
00:06:20,981 --> 00:06:22,750
SO MAYBE IT'S TIME
FOR AN INTERVIEW.

159
00:06:22,783 --> 00:06:24,718
COME ON, EVERYBODY,
GIVE HIM A HAND.

160
00:06:24,752 --> 00:06:26,987
- COME ON OVER, BEN.
- OH, YEAH.

161
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:29,457
SO THIS GUY, BEN WYATT,

162
00:06:29,490 --> 00:06:31,625
