00:06:45,773 --> 00:06:48,809
[farting]

168
00:06:48,842 --> 00:06:51,144
- THAT'S FUNNY.
THAT'S FUNNY.

169
00:06:51,178 --> 00:06:53,447
- HE'S 18,
BECOMES THE MAYOR,

170
00:06:53,481 --> 00:06:56,884
AND THEN BLOWS THE WHOLE BUDGET
ON AN ICE-SKATING RINK.

171
00:06:56,917 --> 00:06:57,718
CITY GOES BANKRUPT.

172
00:06:57,751 --> 00:07:00,688
