- YOU'RE OUT OF THERE.

173
00:07:00,721 --> 00:07:02,122
- WHAT DID
YOU CALL IT AGAIN, BEN?

174
00:07:02,155 --> 00:07:04,958
- [laughing]
WHAT WAS IT CALLED? SAY IT.

175
00:07:04,992 --> 00:07:06,760
- ICE TOWN.

176
00:07:06,794 --> 00:07:08,896
[laughter]

177
00:07:08,929 --> 00:07:10,664
- I WAS JUST A--
I WAS A KID,

178
00:07:10,698 --> 00:07:14,067
AND, UM, WHEN YOU--YOU--

179
00:07:14,101 --> 00:07:17,705
YOU END UP GETTING OUT THERE
AND, UH--AND THERE'S A--

180
00:07:17,738 --> 00:07:19,807
- OH, I REALLY WISH YOU GUYS
COULD SEE THIS GUY RIGHT NOW.

181
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,809
HE IS "DRAUNCHED" IS SWEAT.

182
00:07:21,842 --> 00:07:24,878
- THERE'S--THERE'S ALSO GONNA BE
PONIES AT THE HARVEST FESTIVAL.

183
00:07:24,912 --> 00:07:27,981
- ALL RIGHT, LET'S TAKE A CALLER
FROM DOUCHE NATION.

184
00:07:28,015 --> 00:07:29,883
ALL RIGHT, TALK TO ME, CALLER.
- WHAT'S UP, GUYS?

185
