CAN WE JUST SORT OF--

194
00:07:49,837 --> 00:07:51,839
[video game sound effect]

195
00:07:51,872 --> 00:07:53,907
- GAME OVER, MAN.
GAME OVER.

196
00:07:56,544 --> 00:07:57,511
- NICE JOB, MAN.

197
00:07:57,545 --> 00:07:59,046
